[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/csd4FmM.png[/IMG]

[SIZE="4"][B]OrionLP is a project based on slim. The name Orion was chosen as a representation of the beauty and vastness of world around us (Too much Philosophy, eh? [emoji14]). We started this project for falcon (Moto G), to make a stable Rom which would include Bitsyko layers and important customization. The Rom is built with Uber toolchain which delivers awesome smoothness and is packed with a custom kernel built from ground-up to ensure good performance [WIP].  Needless to say, this project is a product of our hobbies and the love we bore for Android. [/B][/SIZE]

[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/HthZuB7.png[/IMG]

