[B][CENTER][SIZE="4"]Copy the ROM and Gapps in SD card.
Go to your recovery - Wipe Data, Cache and Dalvik Cache.
Install ROM and Gapps zip.
Flash SuperSU zip
Reboot - 1st boot takes around 3-4 minutes. 
Enjoy [/SIZE][/CENTER][/B]

[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/mRUCzVV.png[/IMG]

